                      "html": "<h2>What you will learn</h2><p>Understand where lead data, calls, research, practice, time tracking, and team communication belong.</p><ul><li>Identify the purpose of each core tool</li><li>Keep Sandra as the lead source of truth</li><li>Use Closer Lab for deliberate practice</li><li>Escalate blocked work through the correct team channel</li></ul>"
