                    "content": {
                      "html": "<h2>Learner guide</h2><ul><li>If lead activity is not recorded in Sandra it is not operationally visible</li><li>Use property tools for research and Sandra for relationship history</li><li>Complete assigned tasks and next actions on time</li><li>Ask your manager for the current SOP when a tool workflow changes</li></ul><p>Use the current written SOP and ask your manager when a live process differs from this lesson.</p>"
